main_address_raw_text: 23 pescenicka ulica, kriz, zagrebacka zupanija, 10314, croatia
short_description: veggie is a fruit & vegetable market based in križ, croatia.
long_description: in 2015 veggie was founded on the very edge of the zagreb county in the village of razljev in the municipality of križ, croatia. with our main product asparagus, we also produce other vegetables: blue potatoes, industrial tomatoes, processed as dried tomato in oil with also seasonal vegetables like cucumber, pepper, mangel, carrots, parsley, peas, beet root, green salads and other vegetables according to the wishes of our esteemed customers. in addition to this, on 2000 m2 we have planted a lot of different fruits. for a weekly dose of proven homemade and healthy products - call or contact us
